'''Pad 45''' was a docking pad on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Lok/Legends|Lok]] in the vicinity of [[Brogar's Safe House and Cantina|Brogar's]], a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] and safe house. Around [[137 ABY]], [[Naxy Screeger]] attempted to escape from a [[Bounty/Legends|bounty]] placed on him by [[Rav]] and visited Brogar's to make arrangements. A [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] agreed to discreetly transport Screeger and told him to bring all his [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|creds]] to pad 45.<ref name="Legacy 2">[[Legacy (2006) 2|''Legacy'' (2006) 2]]</ref>

